.TH "stash-by-theblacklotus" "6" "2026-06-13" "Stash User Manuals" ""
.hy
.SH NAME
.PP
\f[B]stash-by-theblacklotus\f[R] - run the Stash 64Kb intro by The Black
Lotus
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\f[B]stash-by-theblacklotus\f[R] [\f[B]\[en]help\f[R]]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
\f[B]Stash\f[R] is a 64\ Kb intro released by \f[B]The Black Lotus\f[R]
at a demoparty in 1997.
It features 3.5\ MB of full-colour graphics and 4\ MB of music sampled
at 16-bit/44\ kHz, all packed into a 64\ Kb executable.
.PP
The production was created by probe, jace, nix, balance, danny, and
sick1/trp.
Running the program requires a Pentium-class CPU or better, a VGA card,
and a Gravis UltraSound with at least 1\ MB of sample RAM.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\f[B]\[en]help\f[R]
Display usage information and exit.
.SH SEE ALSO
.PP
Original release page: <https://www.pouet.net/prod.php?which=3>
.SH BUGS
.PP
No known bugs.
Report packaging issues to the Debian Bug Tracking System.
.SH AUTHOR
.PP
\f[B]Stash\f[R] was created by The Black Lotus (probe, jace, nix,
balance, danny, sick1/trp).
.PP
Packaged for Debian/Ubuntu by Nicolas HOUDELOT <nicolas@demosdebs.org>.
